headline: Bestow Closes $120 Million Oversubscribed Series D Funding, Co-Led by Growth Equity at Goldman Sachs Alternatives and Smith Point Capital
summary: Bestow Inc., a leading insurance technology company, today announced the close of a $120 million oversubscribed Series D funding round, including primary and secondary investments. The round was co-led by Growth Equity at Goldman Sachs Alternatives and Smith Point Capital. In addition to the equity financing, Bestow also secured a $50 million credit facility from TriplePoint Capital.
